Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空…破…斩!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.44,0:18:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.45,0:18:53.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好耶!那些妖魔鬼怪全被赶跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.25,0:19:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些妖怪让这股势力变得越来越强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.48,0:19:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再过些日子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够拯救世界的…
